### Stability
The application now starts without crashing, and navigation between [LandingPage](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/pages/LandingPage.jsx#71-419), [Dashboard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/pages/DashboardPage.jsx#7-441), and [Projects](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/pages/ProjectsPage.jsx#13-187) is restored.
